SUMMARY:Three Days of the Condor | 5X Series: Robert Redford
DESCRIPTION:When CIA researcher Robert Redford finds seven of his colleag
 ues murdered\, he is soon targeted next and is forced to go on the run. N
 ot knowing who to trust and with a merciless hit man (Max von Sydow) clos
 e on his tail\, Redford hides out with a beautiful stranger (Faye Dunaway
 ) as he decides how to outwit the very agency he works for. [117 min\; th
 riller\, drama\; English]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  When CIA researcher Robert Redford find
 s seven of his colleagues murdered\, he is soon targeted next and is forc
 ed to go on the run. Not knowing who to trust and with a merciless hit ma
 n (Max von Sydow) close on his tail\, Redford hides out with a beautiful 
 stranger (Faye Dunaway) as he decides how to outwit the very agency he wo
 rks for. [117 min\; thriller\, drama\; English]</p>
